msgctxt "QL_FironeMini_TerribleThunder_Remove"
msgid ""
"It turns out the <1.se_co>lightning<2.re_co> was drawn to\n"
"Lakeside Stable because of a metal weapon\n"
"stuck on top of the building!\n"
"\n"
"Head back to Cima, and let her know what\n"
"was going on."
msgstr ""

